How long we retain your data:
For those who sign up for daily emails, we retain your data as long as you remain on the list.  You can unsubscribe at any time through the email sent.  When you unsubscribe, all data will be deleted. The email address provided by those who double opt in to our email service is the only personally identifiable information that we keep, only as long as you remain subscribed. Please see the other services privacy policies from the services we use listed above for information on how long they keep data.
What rights you have over your data:
You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you (e.g., your email address as long as you remain on our list). This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes. To make this request, simply unsubscribe from our email list and we will delete your email data.
